<br>
30 delay weapon, 100% haste<br>
New delay = 15<br>
Increase of 1 damage/hit at double attack 100% = 1.3 DPS increase<br>
<br>
16 delay weapon , 100% haste<br>
New delay = 8<br>
Increase of 1 damage/hit at double attack of 100% = 2.5<br>
<br>
